<title>UK: Ex-dividends to take 2.48 points off FTSE, April 7.</title>
<headline>Ex-dividends to take 2.48 points off FTSE, April 7.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-04-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>The following FTSE 100 stocks will go ex-dividend on April 7 and analysts estimate the effect will be to take 2.48 points off the index that day.</p>
<p>							 DIVIDEND	INDEX</p>
<p>							 (PENCE)	 EFFECT</p>
<p>		   COMPANY			  Net   Gross    Gross</p>
<p> * Pearson					 11.10   13.32    0.440</p>
<p> * Peninsular &amp; Oriental Steam	     17.00   21.25    0.765</p>
<p> * Unilever					21.76   27.20    1.278</p>
<p>-- London Newsroom +44 171 542 7954</p>
